data.description: This stunning 4-sided brick home boasts over 3,000 square feet of spacious living and is conveniently located near McDonough Square with easy access to Highway 155.mpeccably Updated: Gleaming LVP flooring and plush carpets throughout, fresh neutral paint, and a brand-new roof (Sept 2020) Two staircases lead you upstairs, offering tons of room to spread out with huge bedrooms and ample closet space. Enjoy a well-equipped kitchen featuring a black and silver appliances dishwasher, built-in microwave, and gas stove (all included!). The kitchen opens to the family room, perfect for entertaining. Unwind in the oversized owner's suite featuring a sitting room, separate tub and shower, and a large walk-in closet. Ceiling fans in every bedroom and the family room add comfort and style. Enjoy a community pool included in the HOA dues. Upstairs bathrooms and pantry boast new flooring.  This home is just 20 minutes from Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport, 15 minutes from Tanger Outlets, and 25 minutes from downtown Atlanta. McDonough's vibrant downtown area with its shops, restaurants, and supermarkets is less than 5 minutes away!
